== Release notes ==

These are the release notes for version 1.1. See [[{{NAMESPACE}}:{{BASEPAGENAME}}/History]] for older releases.

=== New features ===

* Added the '''withoutsuffix''' item to the result records of [[{{NAMESPACE}}:{{BASEPAGENAME}}#mw.ext.dpl.getPages]].
* Added the '''resolve''' option to the [[{{NAMESPACE}}:{{BASEPAGENAME}}#Redirects]] module.
* Added the [[{{NAMESPACE}}:{{BASEPAGENAME}}#Redirectsto]] module.

=== Bugfixes ===

* Page titles containing <code>&</code> characters are now handled correctly.

